---
title: Retro Tex-Mex Nacho Salad Serves 2 | with Chipotle Dressing
description: Everyone's favourite nacho salad is back! Crisp lettuce, black beans and tomatoes get tossed with smoky, creamy chipotle dressing. A flourish of crushed tortilla chips and cheddar cheese completes this re-inspired retro classic.
